text: Østerdal Billag is a Norwegian bus operator operating in Østerdalen in Innlandet. The company also operates in cooperates with Gauldal Billag on a NOR-WAY express bus between Trondheim and Oslo. The company has its headquarters in Tynset. The company was founded in 1973 as a merger between 23 local bus companies and is owned by Gauldal Billag. ==References== Category:Bus companies of Innlandet Category:Companies based in Innlandet Category:Transport companies established in 1973 Category:1973 establishments in Norway Category:Fosen Trafikklag
